OL,7,FWorkers at the Atomic Weapons
OL,8,FEstablishment in Berkshire have
OL,9,Flaunched a 24-hour strike in a dispute
OL,10,Fover pay.
OL,12,FMembers of the Prospect union walked
OL,13,Fout this morning and will be on strike
OL,14,Funtil 7am tomorrow (Thursday 25
OL,15,FJanuary).
OL,17,FThey mounted picket lines outside the
OL,18,Fsite in Aldermaston which supports and
OL,19,Fmaintains the UK nuclear deterrent.
