OL,4,CEstablishment in Berkshire strike over
OL,5,Cpay
OL,7,FThe workers previously voted heavily
OL,8,Fin favour of industrial action in
OL,9,Fprotest at a 6% pay offer.
OL,11,FProspect general secretary Mike Clancy
OL,12,Fsaid: "Our members at AWE have been
OL,13,Fleft with no option but to take this
OL,14,Faction after years of stagnating pay.
OL,16,F"It is simply unbelievable that within
OL,17,Fthe organisation responsible for
OL,18,Fmaintaining our nuclear deterrent
OL,19,Fpeople are struggling with the basic
OL,20,Fcost of living.
