OL,5,Cpay
OL,7,F"We have also seen a disappointing
OL,8,Flack of proper engagement from the
OL,9,Femployer, typified by the pay offer
OL,10,Fbeing presented as a done deal, with
OL,11,Fno rationale given for the number, nor
OL,12,Fany space for negotiation.
OL,14,F"If the Ministry of Defence and AWE
OL,15,Fdon't think again and make a pay offer
OL,16,Fthat reflects the still rocketing cost
OL,17,Fof living, there is a real risk that
OL,18,FAWE will struggle to recruit and
OL,19,Fretain the skills that it needs."
